abstract: Why is “the Scottish play” so hard to get right? Two productions in Britain show why Shakespeare’s shortest tragedy is also his trickiest.
snippet: Why is “the Scottish play” so hard to get right? Two productions in Britain show why Shakespeare’s shortest tragedy is also his trickiest.
lead_paragraph: STRATFORD-UPON-AVON, England — “Macbeth” is Shakespeare’s shortest and most concentrated tragedy, shot through with well-known phrases and images. Why, then, is it so rarely satisfying when performed? You almost feel as if its infamous witches were having their wicked way with this vexed play, four centuries on.

abstract: A woman in Tempe, Ariz., died after being hit by a self-driving car operated by Uber, in what is believed to be the first fatality of a pedestrian from an autonomous vehicle on public roads.
snippet: A woman in Tempe, Ariz., died after being hit by a self-driving car operated by Uber, in what is believed to be the first fatality of a pedestrian from an autonomous vehicle on public roads.
lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO — Arizona officials saw opportunity when Uber and other companies began testing driverless cars a few years ago. Promising to keep oversight light, they invited the companies to test their robotic vehicles on the state’s roads.

abstract: The competition crowned its Season 3 champion on Thursday, and the result was pretty unsatisfying.
snippet: The competition crowned its Season 3 champion on Thursday, and the result was pretty unsatisfying.
lead_paragraph: Well, we’ve come to the end. We’ve been through so much — Milk’s tantrums, BeBe’s speaking in tongues, Shangela’s “Game of Thrones” fan-fic — and yet, so little. This season frontloaded its villains (Morgan McMichaels, Thorgy Thor, Milk), mishandled one hero (Chi Chi DeVayne) and let another (BenDeLaCreme) go on walkabout, and came up short on what’s usually so special about “RuPaul’s Drag Race”: heart and stakes and the sense that lives are being changed. What were we supposed to root for, longer meet-and-greet lines for Kennedy Davenport?

abstract: Of the five who died in the East River crash, some were newcomers to the city, others tourists from as far as Argentina. None were older than 34.
snippet: Of the five who died in the East River crash, some were newcomers to the city, others tourists from as far as Argentina. None were older than 34.
lead_paragraph: A video posted on Instagram Sunday night recorded some of their final moments: Young faces, glowing in the pink light of dusk, smiling wide as their sightseeing helicopter lifted off the ground.

headline_main: On ‘S.N.L.,’ ‘The Bachelor’ With Another Kind of Breakup

abstract: The pornographic actress’s case, seeking to break an agreement to keep silent about an alleged affair with the president, could lead to his having to testify in a deposition.
snippet: The pornographic actress’s case, seeking to break an agreement to keep silent about an alleged affair with the president, could lead to his having to testify in a deposition.
lead_paragraph: In the blur of news coming out of Washington, the legal maneuvers involving a pornographic film actress who says she had an affair with President Trump and the president’s lawyer who paid her hush money may seem like just another reality-show-ready spectacle at 1600 Pennsylvania Avenue.

abstract: The team’s Legion of Boom defense appears on its way to oblivion without having gotten enough credit for just how dominant it was.
snippet: The team’s Legion of Boom defense appears on its way to oblivion without having gotten enough credit for just how dominant it was.
lead_paragraph: It was one of the most important plays for one of the greatest defenses in N.F.L. history, but it has been all but forgotten because of what happened afterward.
